titles.full: Classical Baby (I'm Grown Up Now): The Poetry Show

summaries.short: This HBO Family special presents the world's greatest works of poetry--from Shakespeare to Frost--in a way that children can appreciate.
summaries.full: Poems about love...birds...roses...weather. This HBO Family special presents the world's greatest works of poetry in a way that children can appreciate. From Shakespeare to Frost, the legendary lines are presented via whimsical animation and lovingly read by performers including Andy Garcia, John Lithgow, Susan Sarandon, Jeffrey Wright, and others.

summaries.short: Enjoy lullabies heard around the world in this delightful, transporting mix of music and art.
summaries.full: Featuring lullabies heard around the world--from Cuba to Scotland, Indonesia to Brazil--this "Classical Baby" specials also contains original recordings by contemporary artists and music by some of the greatest classical composers of all time. For the young and the young-at-heart, "The Lullaby Shows" are a delightful, transporting mix of music and art.
